data.description: Welcome to this exquisite three-story haven nestled in the heart of Maywood, IL. This stunning property offers an unparalleled living experience with its grandeur, spaciousness, and elegant design.This expansive home boasts five generously sized bedrooms with 3 of them having their own bathroom providing ultimate comfort and privacy for all occupants.The house features a sleek and contemporary design, showcasing clean lines and premium finishes throughout. Large windows throughout the residence flood the interior with natural light, creating an inviting and airy ambiance.The chef's kitchen is a masterpiece, ample cabinetry, its own separate dining room perfect for entertaining guests.The property offers multiple living areas across its three levels, providing versatility for relaxation, entertainment, and gatherings.Step outside to discover a private backyard space and a gorgeous deck ideal for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply soaking in the sunshine.Situated in Maywood, this residence offers easy access to local amenities, schools, parks, dining, shopping, and transportation options for added convenience.  This exceptional three-story home in Maywood presents an extraordinary opportunity to live in luxury and comfort. Whether you seek ample space for a growing family or desire a sophisticated retreat to call your own, this property embodies modern elegance and timeless appeal. Arrange your private showing today and experience the epitome of upscale living in this magnificent residence!
